                <title id="gdp-chart-title">Interactive chart of Argentina GDP per person, 1990 to 2025</title>
                <desc id="gdp-chart-desc">Choose current US dollars or purchasing-power-parity adjusted international dollars. Move across or click the plot, or use the year slider and arrow keys, to inspect annual values. The shaded 2007 through 2015 period uses the later reconstructed national accounts rather than the figures originally reported.</desc>
